title: Added new features for v1.2 of the game
message:
Added new features for v1.2 of the game

* Each game now starts off with 3 lives. You lose a life each time the
ball misses the paddle and hits the bottom of the screen.
* 2 new levels have been added, giving 5 levels in total.
* A couple of bugs have been fixed - to make sure the "Level 1" text is
always displayed at the top of a new game, and to make sure the smiley
ball doesn't move off the screen.

title: Added new features for v1.1 of the game
message:
Added new features for v1.1 of the game

1) Smiley and sad balls now move when hit
2) The high score is now saved and displayed on screen
3) The ball now starts off a bit more slowly, and speeds up when you
reach a new level.
4) Levels are now numbered and displayed in the top-left corner of the
screen.
